```

in `camera.launch`:

```
<remap from="image" to="/camera1/usb_cam1/image_raw"/>

<remap from="image" to="/camera2/usb_cam2/image_raw"/>
```

defines the cameras

if no camera plugged in, the built in camera will be recognised as one of the cameras.


